{"tid":496201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲Google華裔女工程師 離奇喪命加州海灣","createTime":"2017-12-11T12:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T14:29:38.000Z","uid":88681,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0d9c34d747df0a6fb4e5c2d0679a0e09558fa8","tid":496201,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512989690_f69d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512989690_f69d.jpg&h=e6a30806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加利福尼亞州聖塔克拉拉縣（Santa Clara）法醫證實，本月7日在桑尼維爾(Sunnyvale)海灣步道邊發現的一具赤裸女性浮屍，確認是Google的23歲華裔軟件工程師馬楚楚（Chuchu Ma，音譯）。警方正就其死因展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據美國NBC網站及《世界日報》報道，馬楚楚的屍體是在森尼維爾市莫菲特野外的海灣水面上，被一名騎單車的過路人發現。屍體當時赤裸，面部朝下。警方接報後派出潛水人員將屍體撈起。<br />\n<br />\n雖然法醫只公佈了死者的姓名，沒有發放進一步資料，但通過受害人在LinkedIn網站的個人資料顯示，她是當地山景城的居民，去年畢業於奧斯汀的德克薩斯大學（Univ. of Texas at Austin），隨後任職Google軟件工程師，並曾在Yahoo做過實習生。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，Google已證實馬楚楚的死訊。該公司的一名發言人發表聲明說：「馬楚楚是我們開發產品團隊的優秀軟件工程師。我們對她的去世感到震驚，我們對她的家人和朋友表示最深切的哀悼。」NBC援引其一位同事對她的評價稱，平日裏的馬楚楚「開心積極」、「總是讓別人微笑」。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方對該案的相關細節守口如瓶，僅僅表示目前尚不清楚這名受害人的死亡原因，一切還有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n據網上資料，馬楚楚為一名高材生，高中時曾於2,500名學生中脫穎而出，獲得一個名額僅有5名的獎學金。另外，馬楚楚亦曾成功獲得多個獎學金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171211/57568440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57568440&d=yn3BGvb2U5LlimHHiF7lbgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=60ee6d51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57568440&h=e9f9c87a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171211/57568440</a>"},{"pid":"101dfa2702a39f1c583ab1b7fc0e186e580f5eba","tid":496201,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"23歲咁的樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a8231ae932415a05a380f6bc88943c4706ad76","tid":496201,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"It狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481669f4fb2b2f2aef00c304ddc11b9fca882314","tid":496201,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"唔同中共合作，被自殺姐"},{"pid":"2417a23e2e7b40722d30fd450980a82bfa3be858","tid":496201,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"2cead99532e5df1c1ffceaa7aa94789ea61ae58e","tid":496201,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人沒有一個是無辜的</blockquote><br />\n人地係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da122aa75b199197a7affaf4c2e24e2eb0c63c70","tid":496201,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"支那就支那啦<br />\n<br />\n華乜撚野裔, 好熟呀依家？"},{"pid":"9c87b94f446d3ee19960b1e0eb7ad7a753c7d29c","tid":496201,"uid":41317,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那就支那啦<br />\n<br />\n華乜撚野裔, 好熟呀依家？</blockquote><br />\n華人就一定係大陸架啦咩"},{"pid":"5a5e078235c5f8f6831b6887ae4f9d0a5d654379","tid":496201,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那就支那啦<br />\n<br />\n華乜撚野裔, 好熟呀依家？</blockquote><br />\n華人就一定係大陸架啦咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「華人」就係全球統戰用詞<br />\n大家分清楚！<br />\n<br />\n台灣人就台灣人, 星加坡人就星加坡人, 香港人就香港人, 支那人就支那人<br />\n<br />\n華你老母人"},{"pid":"353dbf9021cba3d9223dc562f3bef4f09d09cc34","tid":496201,"uid":776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:29:38.000Z","